data.description: Come view this cozy 3/2 located in the peaceful country. Minutes away from Matagorda Beach and located in the heart of Wadsworth,  this home sits on a little over an acre of land and has a huge workshop. Plenty of space for livestock or other outdoor pets and close to the post office and convenience store. Home has lots of parking space, a large covered side patio and carport, and a huge wooden porch for those family get togethers. Large fenced backyard with a storage shed and another fenced in area towards the back of property.  Private septic system and Wadsworth Water supplies the water. Utility room is under the covered porch. This delightful home is a country lovers dream and located only minutes away from Bay City.  Come take a look!
